data.description: This cozy home is the perfect place to call your own. With its inviting spacious corner lot and unique features, this home is sure to steal your heart. As you step inside, you're greeted by a warm and welcoming living room with a crackling wood fireplace. The perfect place to relax and unwind after a long day. The kitchen is perfect for cooking, with plenty of counter space and cabinets. enjoy a vintage built oven, and a breakfast bar that's perfect for casual dining. The adjacent dining room is ideal for entertaining guests or hosting family gatherings with enclosed sunroom and inviting back yard. You'll find 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, each with its own unique charm. The master suite features a private bathroom and closet. The quaint backyard has an enclosed patio, mature trees and plenty of space for a pool. It's the perfect place to relax. This home is located in a quiet, family-friendly neighborhood, close to schools, parks, and shopping. It's the perfect place to raise a family or start a new chapter in your life. Recent updates include new roof placed 6 years ago, new windows 2020, and exterior paint 2020.  Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a truly charming home.
